Name: User can navigate to Test Cases page
Description:
Given a user on the home page
    When they click on 'Test Cases' link in header
    Then they should be navigated to the test cases page

Name: API returns 404 for invalid credentials
Description:
Given non-existent user credentials
        When login is attempted via API
        Then the response should indicate user not found

Name: Complete account lifecycle: register, logout, login, delete
Description:
Given a new user
    When they register, logout, login again, and delete their account
    Then each step should complete successfully

Name: User can add product to cart
Description:
Given a user on the products page
    When they add first product to the cart
    And click continue shopping
    And they add second product to the cart
    And click view cart
    Then they should be redirected to the cart page

Name: Products page displays product list
Description:
Given a user navigates to the products page
    When the page loads
    Then the products list should be visible
    And at least one product should be displayed

Name: API returns all products with valid structure
Description:
Given the products API endpoint
    When a GET request is made
    Then it should return a list of products with expected fields

Name: User can search for products
Description:
Given a user on the products page
    When they search for a product
    Then all the products related to search are visible

Name: API returns success for valid credentials
Description:
Given a registered user
        When their credentials are verified via API
        Then the response should indicate user exists

Name: Registration fails for existing email
Description:
Given an email that is already registered
    When a user attempts to sign up with that email
    Then they should see an error message

Name: TC16: Place order after login
Description:
Given a logged-in user
    When they add products, proceed to checkout, and complete payment
    Then the order should be placed successfully

Name: User can login with valid credentials
Description:
Given a registered user
    When they login with valid credentials
    Then they should see their username in the header

Name: Login fails with invalid credentials
Description:
Given a user on the login page
    When they attempt to login with invalid credentials
    Then they should see an error message

Name: Complete account lifecycle via API: register, login, delete
Description:
Given a new user
        When they register, login, and delete via API
        Then each operation should succeed

Name: User can contact us successfully
Description:
Given a user on the contact us page
    When they fill out the contact form
    And click submit
    Then they should see a success message

Name: User can complete full registration flow
Description:
Given a new user with unique email
    When they complete the full registration form
    Then their account should be created
    And they should be able to delete the account

Name: User can logout successfully
Description:
Given a logged-in user
    When they click logout
    Then they should see the login form

Name: TC15: Place order after registration
Description:
Given a new user who just registered
    When they add products and complete checkout
    Then the order should be placed successfully
    And the account should be cleaned up
